EFF leader Julius Malema didn't waste time in refuting Jacob Zuma's claim that he was one of the people who was against recalling Thabo Mbeki. JOHANNESBURG - While President Jacob Zuma was addressing the nation with a response to the ANC's decision to recall him, politicians from opposition parties were tweeting their responses. Economic Freedom Fighter (EFF) leader Julius Malema, of course, didn't waste time in refuting Zuma's claim that he was one of the people who was against recalling Thabo Mbeki and other claims. 